text: Secret #6: Dream - There are as many successes in life as there are graduates here today, if you are willing to dream. #SixSilentSecrets
name: Johnny Isakson

text: Secret #5: Faith - Faith is a series of disappointments held together by singular moments of joy and success. #SixSilentSecrets
name: Johnny Isakson

text: Secret #4: Love – ‘Always remember to love people, and use things – don’t ever use people, and love things.’ -Will Rogers #SixSilentSecrets
name: Johnny Isakson

text: Secret #3: Ethics - Doing right is sometimes the most difficult thing to do, but it is always the best thing one can do. #SixSilentSecrets
name: Johnny Isakson

text: Secret #2: Respect - We’re all different sizes/shapes/ethnicities/creeds, but every1 has something 2 offer our fellow man. #SixSilentSecrets
name: Johnny Isakson
